        "content": "# 1. 加载模型和分词器\n\n\n```python\nmodel_name = \"bert-base-chinese\"\ntokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(model_name)\nmodel = AutoModel.from_pretrained(model_name) \n```\n",
