        "type": "same_doc"
      },
      {
        "content": "# 说明_2\n\n```txt\n[AC]interface Vlan-interface 1   \n[AC-Vlan-interface1]ip address 60.191.99.143 255.255.0.0   \n[AC-Vlan-interface1]quit   \n[AC]interface Vlan-interface 2   \n[AC-Vlan-interface2]ip address 10.249.136.1 255.255.252.0   \n[AC-Vlan-interface2]quit \n```\n\n(6) 使能 DHCP 服务，配置 DHCP 地址池\n\n```txt\n[AC]dhcp enable  \n[AC]dhcp server ip-pool vlan2  \n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]network 10.249.136.0 22  \n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]gateway-list 10.249.136.1  \n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]dns-list 218.201.96.130  \n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]quit \n```",
        "chunk_id": "H3C LA2608室内无线网关 用户手册_10",
        "doc_name": "H3C LA2608室内无线网关 用户手册",
        "type": "same_doc"
      },
      {
        "content": "# 4）编码（encode）\n\n\n编码是将 tokenize $^ +$ convert_tokens_to_ids 合并后的结果，通常还会自动添加特殊符号（如 [CLS] 和 [SEP]），除此之外，还支持 padding、truncate 等功能。\n\nfrom transformers import AutoTokenizer   \n#加载分词器和模型   \ntokenizer $\\equiv$ AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(\"/pretrained/bert-base-chinese\")   \nids $\\equiv$ tokenizer.encode(\"我爱自然语言处理\")   \nprint ids)\n\n输出内容如下\n\n```json\n[101, 2769, 4263, 5632, 4197, 6427, 6241, 1905, 4415, 102] \n```\n\n注：可通过 add_special_token False 参数禁止添加特殊符号\n",
        "chunk_id": "尚硅谷大模型技术之Hugging Face生态_26",
        "doc_name": "尚硅谷大模型技术之Hugging Face生态",
        "type": "cross_doc"
      },
      {
        "content": "# 认证信息\n\n\n请在产品铭牌上查看型号核准代码。\n",
        "chunk_id": "HUAWEI MateStation S 用户指南_27",
